summary: This document contains a certificate of limited liability company resolutions authorizing Deutsche Bank Trust Company Americas to manage accounts for a limited liability company. It outlines the powers granted to authorized signers for account management and the bank's reliance on their instructions.
keyFacts: The document certifies the authority of certain individuals to manage accounts with Deutsche Bank Trust Company Americas.
It specifies that the bank may rely on the instructions of the authorized signers unless notified otherwise.
The document indicates that no one other than the company has any interest in the accounts opened in the company's name.
